programme.desc: Raju, an heir to millions of riches, is devoted to his manipulative stepmother who ploys to extort his wealth. But when Raju's newly-wed wife sees through her plan, she staunchly opposes her, which sets off a war of wits between the two women.

programme.title: SHAKKA
programme.desc: Shakka as a child witnesses the murder of his parents by some businessmen. Years later, he sets out to seek revenge by joining the same gang that killed his parents.

programme.title: SATTA
programme.desc: Anuradha a Delhi based young and dynamic politician moves to Mumbai. Soon she meets Vivek an aspiring politician and marries him. Things take a turn when he is arrested for murder and she has to take his place in the upcoming elections.
